parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear subframe can cause the rear end of the vehicle to fall off, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential fatalities.
symptoms: Loud noises coming from the rear of the vehicle
visual signs of cracks or fractures in the rear subframe mount locations
and the vehicle becoming unsafe to drive.
